author: Unreal Engine
description:
It's that time again! Come join us as we sit down with Tim Sweeney, Wyeth Johnson, Andre Balta and Sjoerd de Jong to chat about some of the highlights of the past year between Unreal Engine, Unreal Editor for Fortnite, Fab and more - plus, the core and heart of everything we do, our community and the incredible things you all have accomplished.
We'll see you there - and happy holidays!
title: Year in Review 2025 | Inside Unreal

author: Unreal Engine
description:
Buckle up as we explore the fast lane of real-time automotive visualization in this action-packed session recorded at Unreal Fest Stockholm. From basic lighting to final cinematic grade quality rendering, it's all about speed, control, and visual impact.

Watch to learn how to craft emotional, lifelike experiences with lighting, materials, and storytelling using the latest features from Twinmotion. You'll get behind-the-scenes insights of client work, use case situations, and high-end personal projects.

Whether you're building cars, environments, or entire moods, this is your launch sequence.
Check out this session designed for artists, designers, and gearheads ready to hit full throttle.

Learn more about Twinmotion here: twinmotion.com

#AutomotiveVisualization, #Twinmotion, #UnrealFestStockholm
title: Launch Control: Accelerating Real-Time Automotive Design | Unreal Fest Stockholm 2025
